## тЪЩя╕П Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|---|---|
| Frontend | HTML, CSS, Vanilla JavaScript |
| Backend | Python, Flask, Flask-CORS |
| Database | MySQL |
| Auth | Session-based login |

---

## тЬи Features

- тЬЕ User Registration & Login
- тЬЕ Session-based Authentication
- тЬЕ Create / Read / Update / Delete tasks
- тЬЕ Task status toggle (Pending тЖТ Done)
- тЬЕ Per-user task isolation
- тЬЕ Dark theme UI with animated background
- тЬЕ Responsive design

