## ЁЯЪА Local Setup тАФ How to Run

### Step 1 тАФ Clone the repo
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/taskflow.git
cd taskflow
```

### Step 2 тАФ Install dependencies
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### Step 3 тАФ Setup MySQL database
```bash
# MySQL-ро▓ login рокрогрпНрогрпБ
mysql -u root -p

# Database create рокрогрпНрогрпБ
CREATE DATABASE todo_app;

# SQL file run рокрогрпНрогрпБ
source database.sql;
```

### Step 4 тАФ Update database config
`database.py` file-ро▓ роЙройрпНройрпЛроЯ MySQL password рокрпЛроЯрпБ:
```python
DB_CONFIG = {
    "host": "localhost",
    "user": "root",
    "password": "your_password_here",  # тЖР роЗроЩрпНроХ рооро╛родрпНродрпБ
    "database": "todo_app"
}
```

### Step 5 тАФ Run the app
```bash
python app.py
```

### Step 6 тАФ Open in browser
```
http://localhost:5000
```

**Default login:** `admin` / `admin123`

---

## ЁЯФМ API Endpoints

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|---|---|---|
| POST | `/api/register` | New user create |
| POST | `/api/login` | User login |
| POST | `/api/logout` | Logout |
| GET | `/api/todos?user_id=1` | Get all todos |
| POST | `/api/todos` | Create todo |
| PUT | `/api/todos/:id` | Update todo |
| DELETE | `/api/todos/:id` | Delete todo |
| PATCH | `/api/todos/:id/status` | Toggle status |

